text: Dagmar Boom (born 01 May 2000) is a Dutch volleyball player, who plays as a receiver/libero. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She plays for Talent Team Papendal. She participated in the 2017 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * CEV profile * https://www.flovolleyball.tv/articles/5066163-5-reasons-to-watch- the-2017-montreux-volley-masters Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch women's volleyball players Category:People from Hoorn
